Squizzy::

Her eyes lit up and her sytems activated.  Her circuits started up 
and power flowed through her.  Her body twitched and jumped as it 
started to come on line.  Her programs that still were active started 
to react to the new board.  The board, had wiped out her memory 
completely.  But her back up memory chips uploaded her bio-techno 
engineering, programming skills and repair abilities. She clentch her 
fist and then relaxed her hand.  She slowly opened her eyes and 
looked around.  She saw Zardus and then looked around the room 
again.  "What's going on? Who are you? Where am I?"  then she closed 
her eyes and realized what she couldn't remember. "Who am I?
